comment: /**  * This method is called by the {@link RegisteredRpcConnection} when the registration is success.  *  * @param success The concrete response information for successful registration.  * @param connection The instance which established the connection  */
code: /**  * This method is called by the {@link RegisteredRpcConnection} when the registration is success.  *  * @param success The concrete response information for successful registration.  * @param connection The instance which established the connection  */ void onRegistrationSuccess(T connection, S success).

comment: /**  * This method is called by the {@link RegisteredRpcConnection} when the registration fails.  *  * @param failure The exception which causes the registration failure.  */
code: /**  * This method is called by the {@link RegisteredRpcConnection} when the registration fails.  *  * @param failure The exception which causes the registration failure.  */ void onRegistrationFailure(Throwable failure).
